# AI Agent Page Plan

## Approach
Full-page conversational AI assistant using Vercel AI SDK with @ai-sdk/google provider.
Rich chat interface with knowledge context from all company data.

## Implementation Steps

1. Install packages: `ai`, `@ai-sdk/google`
2. Create `/app/api/agent/route.ts` — streaming route using `streamText` from AI SDK with full data context
3. Build `/app/(dashboard)/agent/page.tsx` — full-page chat with:
   - Conversation history sidebar (left)
   - Main chat area with markdown rendering
   - Suggested prompts grid when empty
   - Rich message bubbles with timestamps
4. Add "المساعد الذكي" nav item to sidebar with Bot icon
5. Build + verify
